EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
CANARY ISLANDS TO CAPE VERDE AND THE GAMBIA.
DNC 01, DNC 08.
1. 45 FOOT S/V WALKABOUT I, BLUE HULL, UNREPORTED
   LA GRACIOSA (29-15.0N 013-30.5W) TO
   CAPE VERDE (15-06.7N 023-37.0W),
   DAKAR (14-41.6N 017-26.8W)
   AND THE GAMBIA (13-28.0N 016-36.0W).
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP
   A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO MRCC OOSTENDE, PHONE: 325 970 1000,
   FAX: 325 970 3605, E-MAIL: MRCC@MRCC.BE
   OR MRCC LAS PALMAS, PHONE: 349 2846 7757,
   E-MAIL: LASPALMAS@SASEMAR.ES.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2287/15.
